{"tid":173764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底邊撚個開始將尻當鳩? 唸當諗?","createTime":"2017-03-26T11:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T14:53:26.000Z","uid":34889,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d78b91dcf11a6d394b3c6e4996723b78a527afac","tid":173764,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"大佬呀, 尻明明就讀烤, 你鬧人都唔想俾人串返轉頭架? 我屌烤你呀? 轉埋做個吊字我就真係吊撚住你黎烤喇! 做乜撚嘢呀?<br />\n<br />\n唸就仲撚過份, 唸書定唸經呀? 諗嘢就諗嘢啦? 係咪咁撚多人唔柒識字呀屌<br />\n<br />\n仲要個個post都見到! 冇 人 屌?"},{"pid":"00e70f3ca50de6fb925678e9730eb78a18168e01","tid":173764,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"非尻非鳩<br />\n<br />\n正字：㞗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&amp;char=%E3%9E%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fdictionary.pl%3Fif%3Dgb%26char%3D%25E3%259E%2597&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bb1ad6db\" target=\"_blank\">http://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&amp;char=%E3%9E%97</a>"},{"pid":"9fdebdba9cef96dfec8f6dafaddf2dcbd0d3ee97","tid":173764,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"雖然樓主平時低質，又爛口，不過今次認同你，清，你的確講得無錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尻：甲骨文用作地名，又表示人之臀部。从尸，九聲。〔苦刀切〕<br />\n粵音 haau1 或 hou1<br />\n<br />\n鳩：鶻鵃也。从鳥，九聲。〔居求切〕<br />\n粵音 gau1 或 kau1<br />\n<br />\n㞗：《字彙》渠尤切，音裘。男子隂異名。<br />\n<br />\n㞗，寫法為「尸」字入面加個「求」字。根據康熙字典，呢個字讀求（kau4），但一般俗音讀鳩（gau1）。意思指男人嘅性器官，係其中一個粗俗俚語用字。由於唔少電腦唔支援呢個字，所以一般網絡上會以「鳩」字假借渠個音，另外亦有人用「門」字裏面加個「九」字（𨳊）代替。除咗呢兩個外，有啲人以為「尻」字入面有個「九」字，讀「㞗」，用「尻」字表示廣東話粗口㞗，但其實尻字解做髖骨，讀烤（haau1），無論音定意思都同㞗無關。流行用語「硬膠」嘅語源，就係來自「戇㞗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ghmafty.blogspot.hk/2014/08/blog-post_10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fghmafty.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F08%2Fblog-post_10.html&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b1e77cd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://ghmafty.blogspot.hk/2014/08/blog-post_10.html</a>"},{"pid":"89b5995ed2c20c0e506d94da99c3f793c3e6a29f","tid":173764,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5547c0d4df8659560d41454a260b79da036c6e95","tid":173764,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"呢家<br />\nd個"},{"pid":"2ad0343108d553c040876e3b60f8b4e6ce26b071","tid":173764,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢家<br />\nd個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05601dd98e48d5bd9262f10046c9c4a88f8afd72","tid":173764,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:32:53.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/172841\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/172841</a><br />\n<br />\n#89，#102，#105"},{"pid":"1e7e605636f96d051520499a0bca35372fc7460e","tid":173764,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T11:40:19.000Z","msg":"補：<a href=\"http://chardb.iis.sinica.edu.tw/char/U+3797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchardb.iis.sinica.edu.tw%2Fchar%2FU%2B3797&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4387b672\" target=\"_blank\">http://chardb.iis.sinica.edu.tw/char/U+3797</a>"},{"pid":"d0489f5c96c5d89664b830359e60113a8945cc72","tid":173764,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>非尻非鳩<br />\n<br />\n正字：㞗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&amp;char=%E3%9E%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fdictionary.pl%3Fif%3Dgb%26char%3D%25E3%259E%2597&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bb1ad6db\" target=\"_blank\">http://ctext.org/dictionary.pl?if=gb&amp;char=%E3%9E%97</a></blockquote><br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"25e24041d58358ce764c9d2ed0dc421be2946456","tid":173764,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然樓主平時低質，又爛口，不過今次認同你，清，你的確講得無錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尻：甲骨文用作地名，又表示人之臀部。从尸，九聲。〔苦刀切〕<br />\n粵音 haau1 或 hou1<br />\n<br />\n鳩：鶻鵃也。从鳥，九聲。〔居求切〕<br />\n粵音 gau1 或 kau1<br />\n<br />\n㞗：《字彙》渠尤切，音裘。男子隂異名。<br />\n<br />\n㞗，寫法為「尸」字入面加個「求」字。根據康熙字典，呢個字讀求（kau4），但一般俗音讀鳩（gau1）。意思指男人嘅性器官，係其中一個粗俗俚語用字。由於唔少電腦唔支援呢個字，所以一般網絡上會以「鳩」字假借渠個音，另外亦有人用「門」字裏面加個「九」字（𨳊）代替。除咗呢兩個外，有啲人以為「尻」字入面有個「九」字，讀「㞗」，用「尻」字表示廣東話粗口㞗，但其實尻字解做髖骨，讀烤（haau1），無論音定意思都同㞗無關。流行用語「硬膠」嘅語源，就係來自「戇㞗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ghmafty.blogspot.hk/2014/08/blog-post_10.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fghmafty.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F08%2Fblog-post_10.html&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b1e77cd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://ghmafty.blogspot.hk/2014/08/blog-post_10.html</a></blockquote><br />\n得兩三個post 都俾你睇到我份人係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abf285589b96f37ca17d54a6115de2239ffb54a","tid":173764,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢家<br />\nd個</blockquote><br />\n呢家真係有啲人會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df8c5935ac84b2660737a4ff16e8dd4955a1a13","tid":173764,"uid":47888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢家<br />\nd個</blockquote><br />\n呢家真係有啲人會咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有天日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f108d97f47764d63cd53c0deffd19350d1ec906c","tid":173764,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bl